fields.title: Using the Shell
fields.description: Learn how to use Python's shell to play with the language and get help.
fields.content:
Launch the shell with "python".

You can exit the shell by entering "exit()" or "quit()".

You can also exit the shell by pressing CTRL and D.

fields.prompt: Which of the following is an *invalid* string container?
Strings cannot contain numbers or special characters.
